provides for adjustments to and reallocation of cash and stock elections made
by Nalco shareholders, as well as the allocation of Nalco shares owned by
shareholders who fail to make an election, to achieve the overall 30%/70%
cash/stock consideration mix. The stock portion of the purchase price is
expected to be tax-free to Nalco shareholders."
